        <section id="overview" title="Overview">
            <p>In this sub-directory is an XML search engine, where you type Google-like queries like this:</p>
            <tt>myTag:myString</tt>
            <p>The list of features include:<ul>
            <li>final HTML formatting different for each collection in the database </li>
            <li>highlight of:<ul>
              <li>terms of the query </li>
              <li>elements containing terms of the query </li>
            </ul>
            </li>
            <li>history of the preceding queries (click to replay)</li>
            <li>clickable list of tags usable in queries (see here <link href="http://wwbota.free.fr/project/data/data-processing.html">Data prepraration</link> how to generate such a list from an XML schema or even from the XML instance)</li>
            </ul>
            </p>
        </section>
